OL,3,CFormer Navy chief recalls surviving
OL,4,CNazi raid as he celebrates 100th
OL,5,Cbirthday
OL,7,FA former head of the Royal Navy in
OL,8,FScotland has celebrated turning 100 `
OL,9,Fand recalled surviving a Nazi raid on
OL,10,Fthe Arctic Convoy days before his 18th
OL,11,Fbirthday.
OL,13,FVice-Admiral Sir Thomas Baird was born
OL,14,Fin Canterbury, Kent, on May 17, 1924,
OL,15,Fthe youngest of five children in a
OL,16,Fmilitary family, but he said he wanted
OL,17,Fto "live a separate life" and decided
OL,18,Fto go into the Navy, enrolling in
OL,19,FDartmouth College in Devon aged 13.
