OL,7,FHe celebrated his 100th birthday on
OL,8,FFriday with a family dinner party with
OL,9,Fhis two children and their spouses,
OL,10,Fand attributed the secret to his
OL,11,Flongevity to keeping a strict routine.
OL,13,FSir Tom's 41-year Navy career began
OL,14,Faged 17 when he served as a
OL,15,Fmidshipman, a sailor of the lowest
OL,16,Frank, on HMS Trinidad as part of the
OL,17,FArctic Convoy ` a gesture of support
OL,18,Fto the Soviet Union in 1941 after
OL,19,FHitler breached a treaty of non-
OL,20,Faggression made two years earlier.
