OL,7,FSir Tom said: "The Trinidad sank the
OL,8,Fday before my 18th birthday, nobody
OL,9,Fwas thinking about giving me a
OL,10,Fbirthday party. It was flat calm in
OL,11,Fthe Arctic and the ship was evacuated
OL,12,Fabout midnight ` it was bright
OL,13,Fdaylight, because it was sunk in May,
OL,14,F82 years ago.
