OL,7,F"The destroyers torpedoed the ship so
OL,8,Fit sank in a ball of flames. While we
OL,9,Fwere waiting we were sent down to open
OL,10,Fthe hatchets so the Germans couldn't
OL,11,Fpick up secret information, we were
OL,12,Ftaken off the ship by the last
OL,13,Fdestroyer.
OL,15,F"I saw the ship going down ` the last
OL,16,Fbit was the stern with the propellers
OL,17,Fgoing down. My friend took a picture
OL,18,Fon a Brownie camera."
