OL,7,FThe then teenager was evacuated to
OL,8,FIceland and then returned to Greenock,
OL,9,FInverclyde ` making the journey home
OL,10,Fstill wearing a sealskin hat.
OL,12,FHe recalled his mother berating him
OL,13,Ffor losing his luggage before sending
OL,14,Fhim off to rejoin the Navy in Chatham,
OL,15,FKent.
