OL,7,FSir Tom, who has five grandchildren
OL,8,Fand 10 great-grandchildren, retired
OL,9,Fjust before the Falklands War in 1982
OL,10,Fand enjoyed playing golf, spending
OL,11,Ftime with his family and was also
OL,12,Fchairman of the Erskine Hospital for
OL,13,Fveterans, in Renfrewshire.
OL,15,FOf the 44 boys in his term at
OL,16,FDartmouth, He said around 18 of them
OL,17,Fwere killed in their first postings in
OL,18,F1941 aged 17.
