OL,7,FSir Tom said: "I always thought I was
OL,8,Fone of the lucky ones ` to have
OL,9,Fsurvived being sunk once, when most of
OL,10,Fmy colleagues were killed."
OL,12,FHe moved to Scotland permanently in
OL,13,F1965, after meeting his wife Angela,
OL,14,Fwho was from Symington, South Ayrshire
OL,15,F` where he still lives.
