OL,7,FHis career peaked in 1979 when he
OL,8,Fbecame Flag Officer, Scotland and
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland ` the head of the
OL,10,FRoyal Navy there ` and he hosted
OL,11,Fguests including US president Richard
OL,12,FNixon and diplomat Henry Kissinger.
OL,14,FReflecting on his long life, widower
OL,15,FSir Tom said: "I have always been
OL,16,Fagainst the government and my parents,
OL,17,Fand everybody else ` I liked to live a
OL,18,Fseparate life.
