OL,7,F"Most of my older relatives had been
OL,8,Fin the Army but nobody had been in the
OL,9,FNavy, so I decided to join ` I
OL,10,Fcouldn't join the RAF as it hadn't
OL,11,Fbeen invented yet. I did war service
OL,12,Fin the UK, the Mediterranean and in
OL,13,Fthe Far East."
OL,15,FHe keeps a strict routine, which he
OL,16,Fsaid is his secret to longevity, and
OL,17,Fis devoted to his dog Victoria.
