OL,7,FSir Tom said: "I don't have any
OL,8,Fmedicines that I take regularly. I
OL,9,Fhave no food between meals and I sleep
OL,10,Ffrom 11pm until 6am. I don't do any
OL,11,Fspecial exercises, like PT, runs or
OL,12,Fthe gym."
